title: DrivePlus_09_16_2014__VIMEO_Dump_720HD
description:
Bulk dump of all of the new Vimeo Drive+ videos as of 09/16/2014.  Same content as YT, but the max resolution is 720p and a different codec is used for 50% higher bitrate vs. YT 720p.

If you've already seen the 1080 YT version, you're not missing much.  Color looks slightly richer with these Vimeo vids, but some details are still lost from the lower resolution.

Will be seedboxed, and DailyMotion channel filled in with these versions as long as they survive DMCA.

Enjoy.
